_sText:
This is my first CS map in a looong time, last time I made a cs map it was for CS 1.5
Lately ive been working on a few Team Fortress 2 maps but I feelt I wanted to make a nice CS:S map! :D There is also a aim version of the map here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/115547

The theme of the map is inspired by dust and dust2, its symmetrical for perfect balance!

Please give me feedback on what to change etc etc

Hope you enjoy it :D
